 you do me the honor"],[479,583,"of having dinner with me?"],[809,921,"Okay, this has Annie"],[921,1059,"written all over it."],[1059,1217,"Right, definitely."],[1343,1589,"Oh my gosh, Mia has got some charm."],[1593,1722,"She's got three fine looking men"],[1722,1835,"right here in this office."],[1860,1993,"I've seen proposals before,"],[1993,2164,"but never a group one."],[2198,2481,"Could Mia be a serial heart breaker?"],[2527,2615,"It's such a show."],[2652,2727,"It's like they want"],[2727,2865,"everyone to know it's staged."],[2994,3178,"Mr. Wilson, a beautiful"],[3178,3328,"and talented woman like Mia"],[3432,3524,"has a lot of admirers."],[3524,3586,"I mean, this doesn't"],[3586,3657,"surprise me at all."],[3749,3849,"Now you seem to know a lot."],[3912,4058,"Maybe you should be a dating coach."],[4141,4425,"Uh, I must have a fever or something."],[4483,4617,"I'm speaking nonsense."],[4959,5038,"Come with me."]],"31":[[204,308,"Come with me."],[308,329,"What?"],[358,458,"Let go of me."],[458,546,"All people are watching."],[567,667,"What are you doing?"],[688,725,"What?"],[942,1055,"Mr. Wilson must be really"],[1055,1159,"feeling the heat."],[1201,1267,"Mia is"],[1267,1418,"just so lucky."],[1497,1539,"Alright,"],[1543,1601,"show's over."],[1639,1714,"Get back to work."],[2039,2248,"Mia, am I too late?"],[2377,2485,"Can't you just behave?"],[2510,2590,"What did I do?"],[2590,2723,"Yeah, what did you do?"],[2773,2923,"Alex is acting like a lovesick puppy."],[2944,2998,"We've have an army"],[2998,3098,"of admirers at the door"],[3098,3244,"declaring their undying love."],[3257,3328,"Stop it."],[3328,3478,"Okay, Alex thinks of me as his sister"],[3478,3578,"and the guys outside..."],[3578,3641,"Wait."],[3732,3812,"Tyler, we're"],[3812,3870,"getting divorced."],[3912,4062,"What right do you have to question me?"],[4087,4137,"As long as we're"],[4137,4212,"still married,"],[4220,4337,"you're still my wife."],[4379,4429,"Okay, then by"],[4429,4546,"that logic, wh